data.description:
The Charleston style rocking chair front porch welcomes you home to this recently renovated 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home on a quiet cul de sac. The front great room is open to dining area! With a natural flow to the open kitchen and 2nd great room area featuring a gas log fireplace, this is a great space to entertain and welcome guests. With all spacious bedrooms upstairs the layout of this home is very functional with no wasted space! The Master Ensuite Features high trey ceiling, bay window with lots of natural light, a private entrance to the upstairs deck. HUGE walk-in closet, custom detailed double vanity and matching mirror! A garden soaking tub & separate shower to enjoy a luxury spa experience in your own Master Ensuite! The other 3 spacious bedrooms all have great closet space and share a bathroom with custom vanity.

Renter responsible for all utilities.
